OL,3,CCampaigners call for better food
OL,4,Callergy protection in the Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FIn conjunction with The Jersey Food
OL,8,FAllergy Group, they're campaigning to
OL,9,Fbring the legislation they introduced
OL,10,Fin the UK on food labelling - called
OL,11,FNatasha's Law - to the Channel Islands.
OL,13,FIf introduced, it would require all
OL,14,Ffood retailers to display full
OL,15,Fingredient and allergen labelling on
OL,16,Fevery food item made on the premises
OL,17,Fand pre-packed for direct sale ` such
OL,18,Fas sandwiches, cakes, and salads.
