OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Channel, Mr and Mrs
OL,8,FEdnan-Laperouse said: "We are here
OL,9,Ftoday in Jersey to speak with a number
OL,10,Fof eminent people - scientists,
OL,11,Fdoctors, experts - to share our
OL,12,Ffamily's story and the tragedy of what
OL,13,Fhappened to us with a wide audience -
OL,14,Ffrom the catering industry, to
OL,15,Fhospitals, to schools, to local
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
