OL,3,CCampaigners call for better food
OL,4,Callergy protection in the Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,F"The life that we lived with Natasha
OL,8,Ftrying to avoid those allergens is the
OL,9,Flife that these families live today
OL,10,Fhere in Jersey. Eating out was almost
OL,11,Fimpossible. It's a very difficult and
OL,12,Fstressful life, and not at all
OL,13,Finclusive in the food economy."
OL,15,FSpeaking about the death of his
OL,16,Fdaughter, Nadim said: "Natasha died in
OL,17,Ffront of me after nearly an hour of
OL,18,FCPR and two shots of adrenaline from
OL,19,FEpiPens that in this case didn't make
OL,20,Fany difference.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
