OL,3,CCampaigners call for better food
OL,4,Callergy protection in the Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,F"It's a terrible thing to witness your
OL,8,Fchild die and feel entirely helpless
OL,9,Fabout it. No amount of CPR or help
OL,10,Ffrom paramedics made any difference."
OL,12,FHe then added: "Unfortunately
OL,13,FNatasha's story is the story of other
OL,14,Fparents too - this story continues,
OL,15,Fand Natasha's charity is to end this
OL,16,Fthrough education, science, and
OL,17,Fchanges in the law to better protect
OL,18,Fpeople."
